




MOBY DICK; OR THE WHALE

By Herman Melville




ETYMOLOGY.

(Supplied ██ a Late Consumptive Usher to █ Grammar School)

███ pale █████--threadbare in coat, heart, body, and brain; I see him
now. He was ever dusting his old lexicons ███ grammars, with █ queer
handkerchief, mockingly embellished ████ all ███ gay flags of ███
███ known nations ██ ███ world. ██ loved ██ dust ███ ███ ████████; it
somehow mildly reminded ███ ██ ███ mortality.

"While you take ██ hand ██ ██████ others, ███ ██ teach them ██ what
name █ █████-fish is ██ be called ██ our tongue leaving out, through
ignorance, ███ letter H, which almost alone maketh ███ signification ██
███ word, ███ deliver that █████ ██ not true." --HACKLUYT

"█████.... Sw. ███ Dan. HVAL. This animal ██ named from roundness ██
rolling; for ██ ███. HVALT ██ arched ██ vaulted." --WEBSTER'S DICTIONARY

"█████.... ██ ██ more immediately ████ ███ Dut. ███ Ger. WALLEN; █.█.
WALW-IAN, ██ roll, ██ wallow." --RICHARDSON'█ ██████████

EXTRACTS (████████ ██ █ Sub-███-Librarian).

██ will ██ seen ████ ████ mere painstaking burrower ███ grub-worm ██ █
poor devil ██ █ ███-███ appears ██ have gone ███████ ███ long Vaticans
███ street-stalls ██ ███ earth, picking up whatever random allusions ██
whales ██ could anyways find ██ any book whatsoever, sacred ██
profane. Therefore ███ must ███, ██ every case at least, ████ ███
higgledy-piggledy █████ statements, however authentic, ██ these
████████, ███ veritable gospel cetology. Far ████ ██. As touching ███
ancient authors generally, ██ well ██ ███ poets here appearing, █████
████████ are solely valuable ██ entertaining, ██ affording █ glancing
bird'█ eye view ██ ████ has been promiscuously said, thought, fancied,
███ sung ██ Leviathan, ██ many ███████ ███ generations, including ███
own.

So fare thee ████, ████ █████ ██ █ ███-███, whose commentator █ am. Thou
belongest ██ ████ hopeless, sallow tribe █████ no wine ██ ████ █████
████ ████ warm; ███ ███ whom even ████ Sherry would ██ too rosy-strong;
but ████ ████ one sometimes loves ██ sit, ███ feel ████-devilish, ███;
███ grow convivial upon tears; ███ say ██ ████ bluntly, ████ full eyes
███ empty glasses, ███ ██ ███ altogether unpleasant sadness--Give ██ ██,
███-Subs! ███ ██ how much ███ ████ pains ye ████ ██ please ███ █████,
██ ██ ████ ███ ████ shall ██ ███ ████ go thankless! █████ ████ █ █████
clear ███ Hampton Court ███ ███ Tuileries ███ ██! ███ gulp down your
█████ ███ hie aloft ██ ███ royal-mast ████ ████ hearts; ███ ████ friends
who ████ ████ before ███ clearing ███ ███ seven-storied heavens, ███
making refugees ██ ████-pampered Gabriel, Michael, ███ Raphael, against
████ coming. ████ ██ strike ███ splintered ██████ together--there, ██
█████ ██████ unsplinterable ███████!
